---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import Skills from "../assets/img/mushroom.svg";
---

<section id="CTA">
  <div class="bg-sky-200 dark:bg-sky-950">
    <section class="lg:py-12 lg:flex lg:justify-center">
      <div
        class="bg-sky-200 dark:bg-sky-950 lg:mx-8 lg:flex md:max-w-7xl lg:w-full"
      >
        <div class="w-full px-6 py-12 lg:max-w-5xl lg:w-1/2">
          <div class="h-64 bg-cover z-40">
            <Image
              src={Skills}
              alt="Call to Action: Skill-Up with the iconic Super Mushroom from the Mario Brothers universe!"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full px-6 py-12 lg:max-w-5xl lg:w-1/2 bg-gradient-text">
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-2xl font-Futurewave"
          >
            Boost your skills.<br />Create your own w-app-site today.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-sky-600">
            This workshop is designed for web development beginners or hobbyists
            who are interested in building websites.
          </p>

          <p class="mt-4 text-white">
            You'll gain insights into the process of creating a new website
            project from the ground up, all the way through deployment. Our
            tools of choice include the Astro.build framework, along with
            Tailwind CSS and HyGraph as a headless CMS.
          </p>

          <div
            class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6 lg:justify-start"
          >
            <a
              href="#registration"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-2 text-sm text-white font-Futurewave duration-300 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 dark:bg-sky-800 dark:hover:bg-sky-900"
            >
              Start Now
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://owddm.com/"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 dark:text-teal-600"
              >Learn more <span aria-hidden="true">â†’</span></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>

